(- vsize/weight drives fee policy and block admission.) Tj
T*
(- Separate relay optimizations \(for example lean block wire payloads that omit export-only) Tj
T*
(fields like tx_list_full\) improve propagation latency but do not change consensus tx vsize.) Tj
T*
(- For TPS/capacity math, always use consensus tx vsize, not transport JSON byte counts from) Tj
T*
(relay wrappers.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(TPS formula) Tj
T*
(Let:) Tj
T*
(- B = 2,500,000 \(effective vbytes per block ceiling from weight/base caps\)) Tj
T*
(- T = block interval in seconds) Tj
T*
(- F = packing factor \(use 0.95 for practical estimate\)) Tj
T*
(- S = average non-coinbase tx vsize) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Then:) Tj
T*
(- TPS ~= \(B * F\) / \(T * S\)) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Production vs dev timing) Tj
T*
(- Production planning target: T = 120s.) Tj
T*
(- Some dev runs use shorter block intervals for testing. TPS scales linearly with 1/T.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Observed tx shapes \(2026-03-07 logs\)) Tj
T*
(- 1 in / 2 out: vsize=1371) Tj
T*
(- 3 in / 2 out: vsize=1646) Tj
T*
(- 16 in / 2 out: vsize=3428) Tj
T*
(- 31 in / 2 out: vsize=5483 \(older pre-cleanup sample was 10012\)) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Estimated practical TPS at T=120, F=0.95:) Tj
T*
(- 1371 vB -> ~14.44 TPS) Tj
T*
(- 1646 vB -> ~12.02 TPS) Tj
T*
(- 3428 vB -> ~5.77 TPS) Tj
T*
(- 5483 vB -> ~3.61 TPS) Tj
T*
() Tj
